---
description: Security and environment rules
globs:
  - "backend/**/*.py"
  - "frontend/src/**/*.ts"
  - "frontend/src/**/*.tsx"
  - "docker-compose*.yml"
  - ".env*"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Never hardcode secrets, API keys, or tokens.
- Read configuration from environment variables.
- Avoid exposing sensitive backend details to the frontend.
- Sanitize logs and error messages.
- Treat user-generated and model-generated content as untrusted input.
